Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,说到底你的决心也不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,换做是我就会开枪 但你却不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你不愿弄脏自己的手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,已经够了吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经输了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,雷纳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,扔掉你的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,加…加里宁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我不是故意…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,带走
